title: Jenkins and Jonez - Media Day Grab Bag, Rihanna’s Back, and Russell Wilson Is The Worst
itunes:title: Jenkins and Jonez - Media Day Grab Bag, Rihanna’s Back, and Russell Wilson Is The Worst
description:
The guys discuss the various funny things from NBA media days, how excited they are for Rihanna to do the Super Bowl halftime show, Russell Wilson continuing his corny streak, and recap the latest episode of House of the Dragon. #Volume #Herd
